We are open for business and we are following Covid-19 regulations. Stay Safe.

Bayview Windows is a leading Ottawa area dealer and installer of exterior windows, patio doors and entrance doors. 

Serving satisfied customers in Ottawa Valley and surrounding areas for over 30 years, we are focused on providing expert advice, superior products and impeccable services to our customers.

We do WINTER INSTALLATIONS. 

Call for a free in-home consultation, or to schedule an after hours appointment at our showroom.

profile: We're a full service Window & Door sales, service and installation company. We offer high end products with reasonable pricing attached to them. profile:
With Golden Windows, you can reinvent your home and save money by replacing under-performing or drafty windows with new, maintenance free options. Installing energy-efficient windows and doors is an important factor in lowering your energy bill. Our aluminum, wood, and vinyl windows are vanguards of efficiency and easy maintenance.
We manufacture high-quality products in our Kitchener plant and partner with trusted suppliers and dealers, professional builders and renovators to ensure you are completely satisfied with your new windows and doors.

Please explore our product lines for solutions that best suit your needs or visit one of our retail locations in Kitchener, London or Ottawa.
